      "title": "Security forces raid Gotagoma late at night",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The security forces have taken steps to evacuate the protesters who were staying at the entrance and premises of the Presidential Secretariat in Colombo in a joint operation this morning.",
        "Several activists were injured and several others were arrested by the police.",
        "The police, the police special task force and the army have jointly launched this operation.",
        "Sri Lanka security forces have detained several individuals near Galle Face"
